{"article_id":"7f2UtEUHevJx6Wyi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Two people were killed and 116 injured in a crash between an Amtrak passenger train and a CSX freight train in South Carolina early Sunday morning .","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"Amtrak Train 91 , en route to Miami from New York , collided with the CSX train at about 2:35 am in Cayce , South Carolina .","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"The Amtrak train was apparently on the wrong track .","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"The Amtrak train ' s lead engine and some passenger cars derailed ;","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"it was carrying eight crewmembers and 139 passengers .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Those injured were transported to local hospitals ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"according to Lexington county spokesperson Harrison Cahill ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"and injuries ranged from scratches to broken bones .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"About 5,000 gallons of fuel were spilled ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"authorities estimated ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"but that there ' s \" no threat to the public at this time , \"","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Cahill said on Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"The National Transportation Safety Board has been called","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"to investigate .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"This is Amtrak ' s second fatal crash this week .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"The Amtrak train in the collision was on the wrong track ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"South Carolina Gov . Henry McMaster told reporters on Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"the CSX freight train ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"which had no one aboard ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" was on the track","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"it was supposed to be on . \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Amtrak said in a statement","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that CSX owns and maintains the area","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"where the trash occurred :","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"\" CSX controls the dispatching of all trains ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"including directing the signal systems","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"which control access to sidings and yards . \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Robert Sumwalt , chair of the National Transportation Safety Board , told Fox & Friends","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"one of the priorities is to recover data recorders","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to determine the speed of the Amtrak train at the point of collision .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Robert Sumwalt , NTSB Chairman :","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"One priority","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"in investigating Lexington County # AmtrakCrash","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"is recovering recorders","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that will indicate speed upon impact pic.twitter.com/KE7ISifeiY","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"- FOX & friends","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"( @ foxandfriends )","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"February 4 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Derek Pettaway , a passenger on one of the train ' s rear cars , told CNN","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that he was awakened by the impact","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"and helped off the train \" really quickly \" by the crew .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"\" Nobody was panicking , \"","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"He went to the hospital","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"after being discharged with minor whiplash","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"went to a shelter for passengers at Pine Ridge Middle School .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"# AmtrakCrash passengers remain at the Pine Ridge Middle School @ RedCrossSC reception site .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"@ LizardsThicket has provided food","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and @ WaffleHouse has provided coffee for those here .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Passenger related questions ?","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Call the @ Amtrak Info Line at 1-800-523-9101 .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"# LESM # LCSDnews","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"pic.twitter.com/6C3PTEWUIx","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"- Lexington Sheriff","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"( @ LCSD_News )","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"February 4 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"This is the latest fatal incident","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"involving an Amtrak train","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"in recent weeks .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Three people were killed and about 100 injured","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"after an Amtrak train derailed in DuPont , Washington , in December .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"On Wednesday , one person was killed","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"when a train","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"carrying congressional Republicans to a retreat in West Virginia","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"hit a truck near Charlottesville , Virginia .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Amtrak has released a phone number","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"for individuals with questions about passengers on the train","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"to call .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Individuals with questions","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"regarding passengers on train 91","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"can contact us at 1.800.523.9101","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"- Amtrak","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"( @ Amtrak )","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"February 4 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Local reporter Chad Mills reported","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that he was told by a source","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"the casualty number isn ' t expected to rise","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"and \" we dodged a bullet on this one .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"\" A very good source tells me","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"the casualty number should n't rise .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"`` We are very , very lucky , ''","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"I 'm told .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"`` We dodged a bullet on this one . ''","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"@ wis10 # sctweets # BREAKING","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"- Chad K. Mills","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"( @ ChadKMills )","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"February 4 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"White House deputy press secretary Lindsay Walters said in a statement","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"that President Donald Trump had been briefed on the incident","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"and is receiving regular updates .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"\" Our thoughts and prayers are with everyone","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"that has been affected by this incident , \"","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"she said .","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"The president also addressed it on Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"My thoughts and prayers are with all of the victims","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"involved in this mornings train collision in South Carolina .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Thank you to our incredible First Responders","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"for the work","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"they ' ve done !","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"February 4 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"The exact cause of the crash , or how fast either train was going at the time of the collision .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":208,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":193,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":162,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":119,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":14,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":116,"right":117,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":112,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":109,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":107,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107